头增加参数校验：\n  ```go\n  if req.ReceiverId == "" || req.ReceiverId == sender
Str {\n      return nil, status.Error(codes.InvalidArgument, "invalid receiver")
\n  }\n  if strings.TrimSpace(req.Content) == "" {\n      return nil, status.Err
or(codes.InvalidArgument, "content is empty")\n  }\n  ```\n- **依据**: `docs/arc
hitecture/layers.md` 第 10.3 节标准错误码映射，`biz.ErrInvalidArgument` 应对应 `
