：校验消息属于目标会话\n+func (uc *IMUseCase) MarkAsRead(ctx context.Context, co
nvID string, msgIDs []string) error {\n+    msgs, err := uc.imRepo.GetMessagesBy
IDs(ctx, msgIDs)\n+    if err != nil {\n+        return err\n+    }\n+    validI
Ds := make([]string, 0, len(msgs))\n+    for _, m := range msgs {\n+        if m
.ConversationID == convID {\n+            validIDs = append(validIDs, m.MessageI
D)\n+        }\n+    }\n+    // 仅对属于该会话的消息创建回执\n+    return uc.imR
epo.BatchCreateReadReceipts(ctx, validIDs)\n+}\n+```\n+\n+#### 基础参数校验\n+\n
+Biz 层应对业务敏感参数进行合法性检查，不依赖数据库的被动约束：\n+\n+| 校验类型 
| 示例 | 失败返回 |\n+|----------|------|----------|\n+| 空值检查 | `ReceiverId`
